title: Person of Interest 2x08 ending
author: George Finch
comment: I guess the interesting part of this is that Michael and Carrie are married in real life and Michael just got paid to kiss his wife. That must be some kiss.
Michael and Carrie bring so much light into my life

You will look for me and I'll be gone 💔
